name: Ancient Star Dragon
text:
1 Tuner + 1+ Non-Tuner Monster.
For this card's Synchro Summon, you can treat 1 "Ancient Gear" monster you control as a Tuner. This card's name becomes "Ancient Gear Golem" while on the field or in the GY. Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can target 1 face-up card you control: Once during this turn, it cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects. If this card attacks, your opponent cannot actiate any Spell/Trap cards until the end of the Damage Step. If this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage.
